'''
This folder contains the Human Body in the Wild (HBW) dataset.
We provide the test and validation set images and keypoints and 
the validation set smplx alignments.


images & keypoints
------------------
These folders contain the images and OpenPose keypoints, respectively. The naming convention is:
    images/[split]/[subject folder]/[image filename]
    keypoints/[split]/[subject folder]/[keypoint filename]
The subject folder naming convention is:
[subject id]_[number of image taken in the lab]_[number of images taken in the wild]


smplx
-----
Alignments of each subject in SMPLX topology (10475 vertices).


Citation:
---------
@inproceedings{Shapy:CVPR:2022,
  title = {Accurate 3D Body Shape Regression using Metric and Semantic Attribute},
  author = {Choutas, Vasileios and M{\‚Äùu}ller, Lea and Huang, Chun-Hao P. and Tang, Siyu and Tzionas, Dimitris and Black, Michael J.},
  booktitle = {Proceedings IEEE/CVF Conf.~on Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (CVPR)},
  month = jun,
  year = {2022},
  month_numeric = {6}
}

'''
